<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Devoutly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Devoutly,</orth> with devotion, earnestly: <cit><quote>she d. dotes, dotes in idolatry,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.109" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 109</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>prayed d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 4.1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 1, 84</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. to be wished,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 84</bibl></cit>.
